      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es darrifchu to Krohni\nnitziqü/ nitziqü/ nitziqü/ ka\ntam buhs nieueeka buht/ kamehr\ntas nahk/ kam tas peederr/ tam\nes to dohfschu."
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tu Zilweka Behrns/\nfluddina un fakki: Ta fakka tas\nKungs KUNGS no Ammona\nBehrneem/ un no winzu Nee-\nwafchanas: Ta tafkt: Tas Soh-\nbins/ tas Sohbins irr iswilfts/\ntas irr us Kaufchanu afs dar-\nrihts/ ka taim buhs nomaitaht/\nun ka taim buhs spihdeht."
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tavehz ka tee tew apla-\nmas Parahdischanasredf/ ka tee\ntew Mellus fluddina/ ka tu no-\ndohfs tohpi lihds ar to eewaino-\ntu Besdeeaign Kakleem/ kurru\nDeena nahze/ kad tas Noseegu-\nma Laiks pa Gallami bija."
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jepfchu tas Sohbins at-\nkat Maksis greestohs/ tomehr es\ntewi fohtifchu tai Weetâ/ fur tu\neffi radrihts/ tai Walsta tawag\nPeemahjofchanas."
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es isgabfsichu pahr te-\nwi mannu Dusmibu/ es uspub-\ntifchu prett tewi to ugguni man-\nnas Bahrsibas/ un nodohfschu\ntew Zilwekeem Rohâ/ kas de-\ndstia un fainaita."
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu buhsi ugguntin par\nBarribu/ taws Affins tezzehs\nSemnes Widdü/ un tewis ne\ntaps wairs peeminnechts/ jo es\n16 KUNGS esuu to runnajs."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N ta KUNga Wah-\nnotikee us man/ un f\nzija:"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu tad ak Zilweka Behr-\nne gribbi tu to affinaizn Vi-\nfafhu teefaht? ne gribbi tu to t-\ntaht! un winnaí rahdiht wi-\nwinna Negantibas."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sakki tad/ ta fakka\nKungs KUNgs: Ak Pilafahf-\nkas tawa Widdü Affinis isle-\nta winna Laikam nahkt bu-\nun kas Suhdu-Deetwas pr-\nfew pascbu darra/ un few-\ngahna."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zaur tawu Affini/ ko\neffi tslehjis/ effi tu noseedsigs t-\npis/ un ar taweem Suhdu-D-\nweem/ ko tu darrijs/ effi tu\ngahnijees/ un effi tawas Dee-\nlizzis tuwu nahkt/ un tu effi\nwos Gaddos nahzis. Tad\nefinu es tewi teem Pagane-\nnodewis par Neewafchanu/\npar Apfmeekli wislahin Sa-\nniehm."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tik labbi kas tuwu un\ntaktu no tewim irr/ tewi-\nfinees/ tewi/ kam neschkil-\nSlawa un leelas Apbehdfnas-\nnas irraid."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Redsi/ Israeka Leel-Ku-\nirr ceefch tewim/ itweens zik sp-\ndams Affini isleet."
    }
  ],
